<h3 id='http-request-2'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>DELETE http://example.com/kittens/&lt;ID&gt;</code></p>
<h3 id='url-parameters-2'>URL Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>ID</td>
<td>The ID of the kitten to delete</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
